parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The tailgate opening while driving can cause damage to the tailgate, loss of cargo, and potentially lead to accidents.
The failure of the electrical system can cause loss of motive power, electrical issues with accessories, and safety risks.
symptoms: front crash sensors going off without obstacles
loss of Google connection on Starlink.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlight and interior lighting system can cause reduced visibility while driving, especially at night, and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Complete failure of headlights and interior lighting

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the HVAC system can cause discomfort and distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Unwanted reduction in front HVAC blower speed
auto AC not working as designed
hot air coming from vents when AC is off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents, and loss of safety warning chimes.
symptoms: Intermittent loss of audio through speakers
shutting off the vehicle for an extended period resets the system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, stranding the driver and potentially leading to accidents.
The uncommanded lowering of the tailgate can cause cargo to fall out of the vehicle, potentially leading to accidents, damage to the vehicle, or injury to pedestrians or other drivers.
symptoms: The tailgate lowers or opens without being commanded
resulting in damage to the tailgate or loss of cargo.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended opening of the tailgate while driving can cause objects to fall out of the bed, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or damage to other vehicles.
symptoms: The tailgate opens unexpectedly while driving
and can cause loss of cargo or damage to the tailgate and surrounding components.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Spontaneous Shattering of Rear Window or Sunroof
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the rear window or sunroof can cause a hazardous situation, potentially leading to injuries or accidents.
symptoms: The rear window or sunroof shatters suddenly
and can cause damage to the vehicle and surrounding components.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unwanted Activation of Remote Tailgate Drop Function
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The accidental activation of the remote tailgate drop function can cause the tailgate to open unexpectedly, potentially leading to accidents or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The tailgate opens unexpectedly due to accidental activation of the remote tailgate drop function

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and uncontrolled increase in volume of the Bose radio can cause a hazardous situation, potentially leading to accidents or distractions while driving.
symptoms: The Bose radio suddenly increases in volume to maximum levels
making it difficult or impossible to turn it off or adjust the volume.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The contamination of the diesel fuel system with DEF (Diesel Exhaust Fluid) can cause engine damage, stalling, or loss of power, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: often accompanied by error codes or warning messages.
